title: Live from San Diego (ACS October 31)
itunes:title: Live from San Diego (ACS October 31)
description: Adam, Gina and Bryan are live at Mic Drop Comedy in San Diego, CA. They talk about how much Adam enjoyed the movie Paddington and pay compliments to the city of San Diego.The gang then plays a Halloween-themed round of Blah Blah Blog before Gina reports the news. Lastly, Adam invites a worship pastor on stage to pull balls for a round of "Adam Carolla is Unprepared."
